WEBVTT

00:00:55.399 --> 00:00:56.039
Zhao Qishan

00:00:57.079 --> 00:00:57.880
Don't do anything rash

00:00:58.039 --> 00:01:00.159
One hour later at the pier warehouse

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:03.479
Take your wife and child home while you're at it

00:01:07.359 --> 00:01:08.480
Zhao Qishan

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:18.280
Zhao Qishan

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:19.840
I brought the person

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:21.040
Look closely

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:22.799
Safe and sound

00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:32.280
You have to keep your word too

00:02:04.319 --> 00:02:06.319
Mr. Tan, you've suffered

00:02:17.199 --> 00:02:17.719
Go

00:02:21.639 --> 00:02:22.599
Your wife and child

00:02:22.759 --> 00:02:24.400
are in the car outside the warehouse's back door

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:37.360
You're awake

00:02:39.439 --> 00:02:40.240
Mr. Zhao

00:02:41.199 --> 00:02:42.240
You saved me again

00:02:44.240 --> 00:02:45.159
You're too kind, Mr. Tan

00:02:45.719 --> 00:02:48.240
Consider this an investment on my part

00:02:50.240 --> 00:02:51.639
Mr. Zhao, what do you want?

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:58.319
I haven't decided yet

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.319
But with your strength, Mr. Tan

00:03:00.319 --> 00:03:02.000
helping a brother do some small business

00:03:02.319 --> 00:03:03.719
shouldn't be difficult

00:03:05.759 --> 00:03:06.960
I remember you said

00:03:07.639 --> 00:03:08.639
we are friends

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:11.000
Of course

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:13.479
Since we are friends

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:17.039
Mr. Tan, for your trip to Taicheng

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.759
I will provide full escort and protection

00:03:20.439 --> 00:03:21.240
What do you think?

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:26.919
I couldn't ask for more

00:03:55.039 --> 00:03:57.240
Mr. Zhao, what is this place?

00:03:58.000 --> 00:03:58.800
Mr. Tan

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:01.520
I just bought a piece of land here recently

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:05.240
I plan to build a comprehensive

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:06.680
large-scale startup park here

00:04:08.439 --> 00:04:09.360
Here there will be

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:11.199
countless star industries incubated

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:12.599
In the future

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:15.680
this place will gather all the talent in Taicheng

00:04:17.920 --> 00:04:18.720
Mr. Tan

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:20.839
I said

00:04:21.839 --> 00:04:24.639
I need to use your abilities to do some small business

00:04:25.480 --> 00:04:27.079
I look forward to your joining

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:29.480
Let's develop this land together

00:04:31.920 --> 00:04:32.800
It's a great honor

00:04:33.879 --> 00:04:35.439
But I have a request

00:04:36.120 --> 00:04:36.720
Please speak

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:40.319
Our group is a listed company

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:41.639
My father has requirements for

00:04:41.639 --> 00:04:43.040
all the projects we participate in

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:45.600
We absolutely cannot do illegal business

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:48.040
Nor can we make the news because of business

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:50.879
And we cannot go to prison

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:52.720
Can you achieve this?

00:05:05.839 --> 00:05:07.800
You're talking nonsense again

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:09.920
I really

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:11.519
Liar

00:05:12.879 --> 00:05:14.240
You are a liar

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:15.040
Miss Asi

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:18.199
Can you take this crazy woman

00:05:18.199 --> 00:05:19.319
upstairs?

00:05:20.759 --> 00:05:22.199
I don't want to be alone

00:05:23.439 --> 00:05:24.279
Auntie Ma Shan

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:26.120
I'll take you back to your room

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:27.560
How about this

00:05:28.519 --> 00:05:29.639
I'll accompany Auntie Ma upstairs

00:05:33.439 --> 00:05:33.920
Tonight

00:05:34.439 --> 00:05:35.439
I will take care of Auntie Ma

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.439
Auntie, let's go

00:05:38.439 --> 00:05:39.959
Okay, okay

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:40.800
Wait

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:46.639
Miss Li

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:51.639
We've finished telling our stories

00:05:53.480 --> 00:05:54.240
What about yours?

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.480
Since we will be here

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:06.600
until the will is announced tomorrow afternoon

00:06:07.319 --> 00:06:08.480
it's not too late to tell it tomorrow

00:06:09.439 --> 00:06:11.240
Why keep everyone in suspense?

00:06:13.199 --> 00:06:14.720
So everyone is looking forward to it this much

00:06:15.439 --> 00:06:17.040
That really exceeds my expectations

00:06:17.759 --> 00:06:18.639
I thought

00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:21.600
this was just some after-dinner entertainment

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:24.399
That's why everyone was lying

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:25.560
What do you mean?

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.319
Just what it means literally

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:39.480
Since tonight is a story-fabricating session

00:06:39.959 --> 00:06:42.439
then my story can also be true or false

00:06:43.439 --> 00:06:45.480
But I don't want to make up a story right now

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:47.199
to waste everyone's time

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:51.439
Let's end it here for tonight

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:53.600
As for my story

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:55.839
since I promised

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:57.240
I will definitely tell it

00:06:58.920 --> 00:06:59.639
Auntie, let's go

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:12.279
I'm tired of listening to stories. Bye-bye

00:07:29.279 --> 00:07:30.040
Auntie Ma

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:32.079
You get some rest first

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:34.120
When you wake up tomorrow

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.480
we'll be able to leave here

00:07:40.399 --> 00:07:41.279
Miss Li

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:44.879
Can you tell me your story?

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:13.439
Inspector Qi

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:17.000
Are you alright?

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:19.759
I'm fine

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:25.240
Ma Shan is asleep

00:08:25.879 --> 00:08:26.600
She's asleep

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:28.720
Do you have a moment?

00:08:29.319 --> 00:08:30.199
Walk around with me a bit more

00:08:43.279 --> 00:08:44.080
Inspector Qi

00:08:44.639 --> 00:08:45.840
I don't want to beat around the bush with you

00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:49.080
I know you're definitely here to find the truth

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:50.200
You might as well speak plainly

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.240
I remember Asi said

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:57.679
Zhao Qishan didn't allow anyone into this study

00:08:58.519 --> 00:08:59.279
Before this

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:01.879
when the police swept this room

00:09:02.519 --> 00:09:03.360
apart from Zhao Qishan

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:05.000
they didn't find a second person's fingerprints

00:09:07.480 --> 00:09:09.039
Did he clean it himself?

00:09:09.919 --> 00:09:10.840
What are you trying to say?

00:09:11.679 --> 00:09:13.320
My brother's inheritance

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:16.320
should have been entirely inherited by me

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:20.879
Lawyer Luo notified me

00:09:21.639 --> 00:09:22.840
so I had to be here

00:09:23.919 --> 00:09:24.919
If I get any money

00:09:26.159 --> 00:09:27.159
I don't need that share

00:09:28.399 --> 00:09:29.080
Ah Hai

00:09:29.799 --> 00:09:31.639
Don't worry, I'll give it all to you

00:09:35.399 --> 00:09:36.519
If I get a share of the money

00:09:36.519 --> 00:09:38.000
I can also give it to Mr. Zhao Qihai

00:09:39.559 --> 00:09:40.320
However

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:45.120
if my share is in Di Fu's will

00:09:45.639 --> 00:09:46.360
and I transfer it to him

00:09:46.360 --> 00:09:48.960
wouldn't that be disrespectful to the deceased?

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:50.720
Don't mention that witch

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:51.679
If I had killed her sooner

00:09:51.679 --> 00:09:52.919
none of this would have happened

00:09:52.919 --> 00:09:54.720
Zhao Qihai, can you stop slandering Di Fu?

00:09:56.879 --> 00:09:57.799
Alright, alright

00:09:58.559 --> 00:09:59.639
Here you go again

00:10:01.879 --> 00:10:04.440
Can't we all sit down and have a nice chat?

00:10:05.919 --> 00:10:07.799
There's nothing that can't be resolved

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:09.720
Sit down

00:10:16.240 --> 00:10:19.799
My sister's case has already been closed as a suicide

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:23.200
But the police haven't announced the motive

00:10:24.120 --> 00:10:25.639
I don't believe my sister would commit suicide

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:28.039
Inspector Qi

00:10:30.559 --> 00:10:31.519
If you are willing

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:33.559
to share the clues you've found with me

00:10:34.279 --> 00:10:36.039
I can also bring out the information I have

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:37.200
to exchange with you

00:10:37.759 --> 00:10:38.480
There's no need for that

00:10:39.519 --> 00:10:40.799
You are the family of the deceased

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:44.320
You have the right to know

00:10:44.879 --> 00:10:45.519
Old Qi

00:10:46.399 --> 00:10:48.440
I've decided to take charge of this case personally

00:10:49.679 --> 00:10:51.440
Actually, the case isn't that complicated

00:10:53.039 --> 00:10:54.600
The wife, Di Fu, had leukemia

00:10:54.600 --> 00:10:56.120
The husband would rather die with her

00:10:56.279 --> 00:10:57.519
He asked his wife to kill him

00:10:57.519 --> 00:10:58.279
and then she committed suicide

00:10:58.759 --> 00:11:01.000
Then according to what you're saying

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:03.519
what is this He Jiarong trying to hide?

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:04.679
Perhaps

00:11:05.639 --> 00:11:08.600
It's great to be a superintendent in a big city

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:10.039
You have to think about the higher-ups

00:11:10.519 --> 00:11:12.639
Zhao Qishan has worked in Taicheng for so many years

00:11:12.639 --> 00:11:13.600
His roots run deep

00:11:13.759 --> 00:11:14.639
From top to bottom

00:11:14.639 --> 00:11:15.720
it's all intertwined

00:11:16.759 --> 00:11:18.000
Actually, I have a question

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.840
Why do you hate Di Fu so much?

00:11:21.639 --> 00:11:23.440
She was your sister-in-law

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:24.279
Ah Hai

00:11:27.159 --> 00:11:27.720
Ah Hai

00:11:37.080 --> 00:11:37.679
Ah Hai

00:11:41.759 --> 00:11:43.440
I'm asking you why you hate Di Fu

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:47.399
She was always between me and my brother

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:49.720
driving a wedge between us

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:52.399
Do you believe your sister killed Zhao Qishan?

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:56.399
I've seen the autopsy report

00:11:57.679 --> 00:11:59.440
Zhao Qishan took a large amount of drugs

00:12:00.039 --> 00:12:01.440
which caused respiratory arrest and death

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:04.519
Then tell me, why did the killer

00:12:05.240 --> 00:12:06.799
stab him so many times?